HEADWORD: knock-knee
<hw>knock"-knee`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A condition in which the knees are bent in so as to touch each
other in walking; inknee.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> knock-knees, genu valgum.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

